4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that provides a comprehensive learning experience in the field of AI and machine learning. The course is designed for beginners with no previous knowledge required. It aims to equip students with the skills to start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models.

The course is 16 weeks long and includes 3 classes per week. Class sizes are limited to a maximum of 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate.

The instructors for this course are Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. They have extensive experience in the field of AI and machine learning, holding PhDs in Artificial Intelligence and Robotics & Artificial Intelligence, respectively.

The course covers a range of topics including Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. They will explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models.

Throughout the course, students will practice solving real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. They will also learn about the complete lifecycle of AI projects, from development to deployment and maintenance, with a focus on privacy and security.

For more information about this course, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning)
